Af - an application framework
===========

setting up papertrail

#### install remote_syslog

sudo gem install remote_syslog

#### create /etc/log_files.yml

files: 
  - /var/log/nginx/*.log
  - /var/log/af/*.log
  - /home/rails/wac/shared/log/*.log
destination:
  host: logs.papertrailapp.com
  port: XXXX

#### start remote_syslog
sudo remote_syslog

####
set up log rotation

